item.title: CVE-2021-36192|2024-08-04T00:54:50.127Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortimanager
item.description: An exposure of sensitive information to an unauthorized actor [CWE-200] vulnerability in FortiManager 7.0.1 and below, 6.4.6 and below, 6.2.x, 6.0.x, 5.6.0 may allow a FortiGate user to see scripts from other ADOMS.
